title: Implant Identifier
description:
Implant Identifier allows for INSTANT identification of any common hip, shoulder, knee, elbow, ankle or wrist implant, based only on an x-ray image. The app uses industry-leading artificial intelligence (AI) technology to scan and match your implant with the closest similar implants from our implant library. 

After selecting the matching implant, users can manually confirm the match to help our AI algorithm continue to improve in accuracy. As our algorithm improves over time, it will theoretically be able to identify any implant with up to 99% accuracy. The future is bright for orthopaedic implant identification. Join us, today!

Additional Features:
-Search through the world's largest orthopaedic implant x-ray library
-Access the official Surgical Technique for any implant by tapping the manufacturer name
-Submit new implants to help our library continue to grow
-Request manual identification of an unknown implant
